The relationship between observed and predicted CH4 (pCH4
                        ) production are presented for Molly and Karoline models using the fixed and mixed model regressions (Figure 1 and Figure 2

                        ). The fixed model regression for Molly predictions was


                              CH4 (g/d) = 0.94 (SE ± 0.022) × pCH4 (g/d) + 31 (±6.9) with RMSPE = 45.0 g/d (14.9% of observed mean).
